songs.lyrics:
Marina:
(It's hard to admit)
Ohhh
(But I need to be honest)
Ohh

Chorus:
I know you have a hard time believing this
But yesterday I had a bliss
While I did something you might think is sick
I Drank more than a lick
OF BLEACH (yeehaw)

Oh oh oh oh
You do not know
The great taste of bleach
YUMMM

Lana del Rey:
Drinking all of your bleach
In more than five minutes
This is my idea of fun
Drinking all of your bleachhhh

(mmmmh)
And now I and Marina will go on to drink a lot of bleach
But the Bleach is in wine glasses
So no one will suspect a thing!
songs.title: Enjoy Your Bleach
